{"tid":2427244,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"長文分析：打疫苗應該為自己，定係為屋企人？意義何在？","createTime":"2021-02-28T15:55:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T16:40:41.000Z","uid":61806,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"49074c34d0c33b13c6fc194a3f12f32806f2834c","tid":2427244,"uid":61806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T15:55:31.000Z","msg":"今日我去私家醫院探病，聽到隔離床個病人家屬問醫生打邊隻疫苗好，個醫生嘅解釋都幾有道理，所以想同各位絲打巴打分享吓。嗰醫生就咁樣講嘅：<br />\n<br />\n全世界嘅疫情咁嚴重，當然要打疫苗啦。而家香港暫時只得兩隻疫苗揀，簡單啲嚟講，就係德國貨BioNtech同國產貨科興。<br />\n<br />\n德國貨保護效果似乎好啲，不過預咗打針之後一兩日會短暫針口痛肌肉痛頭痛同埋發燒，暫時喺以色列英國同美國，打咗幾千萬人，都未有報道非常奇怪而嚴重嘅副作用。而啲所謂嘅死亡報告，世衛專家睇過都話冇關係。<br />\n<br />\n而國產貨呢，保護效果似乎差少少，不過可能打針之後嘅反應會少啲，至於嚴重副作用，國家就話冇。<br />\n<br />\n其實打邊隻針，絕對係個人化嘅選擇。不過打之前，最好先問清楚自己打針嘅目的：<br />\n<br />\n1）究竟你係為自己打針定係為屋企人打針？如果為自己，只要衡量過保護效果同埋潛在副作用就可以決定。如果係為屋企人，例如唔想傳染俾老人家或者小朋友，咁其實應該揀保護效果勁嗰隻。<br />\n<br />\n2）如果你係想唔使再戴口罩，咁就sorry啦，無論你打咗邊隻針，短期內都唔可以除低口罩。如果你屋企老人家心急打針係為咗可以除口罩，咁你不如叫佢唔好打啦，隨時會有反效果。<br />\n<br />\n3）如果你係想去旅行，唔使俾人哋隔離，咁你就要肯定，你所打嗰隻針，一定要人哋國家承認。如果唔係打完都冇用。<br />\n<br />\n4）如果你屋企有老人家有長期病患，即係屬於高危一族，你又決定唔到老人家打邊隻針最好。其實最簡單嘅方法，就係同老人家住嘅人同埋照顧佢嘅人，全部打保護效果最好嗰隻針。因為大部份老人家嘅感染，其實都係屋企人傳染嘅。咁打咗針嘅人就會成為老人家嘅保護罩，變相你唔使即刻決定同老人家打邊隻針先，可以睇定啲情況再算。<br />\n<br />\n5）其實無論係德國疫苗嘅定係中國疫苗嘅研究，結果資料都可能會有錯。所以最好觀察其他已經快速打咗大量疫苗國家嘅報道。德國貨就最好觀察以色列，中國貨就最好觀察智利。以色列同埋智利都係暫時世界上打針最快嘅國家之一，不過一個打德國貨，另一個就支持國產貨。而且呢兩個國家都係民選政府，同埋兩隻 疫苗生產地都唔係自己國家，冇理由要同你隱瞞資料。<br />\n<br />\n6）暫時以色列嘅資料就非常正面，估計三月底就會再報告有關德國疫苗嘅安全資料，到時候九百萬人打咗針之後有冇奇怪嘅嚴重副作用就應該知道，除非以色列政府有心隱瞞啦。<br />\n<br />\n7）智利就二月初開始同啲國民打科興疫苗，預計幾個月之內會打成五百萬人口，如果隻疫苗真係有效，四月份就應該開始見到疫情受到控制，同埋觀察到有冇實際嘅嚴重副作用。<br />\n<br />\n多謝大家睇到呢度，以下自由討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757617549ae6cd685e7c6c973a0a3aebe2c0cd50","tid":2427244,"uid":61806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T15:56:14.000Z","msg":"自推10連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f07e60319a618d117cff3e351a68e534e90ebbf","tid":2427244,"uid":61806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T15:56:25.000Z","msg":"自推10連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e69fd637240f6fe7b9b175984a368218d680a641","tid":2427244,"uid":61806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T15:56:45.000Z","msg":"自推10連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bebc602737dc97d89fa49df6c0e65396a8b43c61","tid":2427244,"uid":61806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T15:57:06.000Z","msg":"自推10連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48e0b5194a597d4ddb837283b687838567af0999","tid":2427244,"uid":61806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T15:57:22.000Z","msg":"自推10連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96b5787e2a7d4d69be6b205277217b941b1e93fb","tid":2427244,"uid":61806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T15:58:02.000Z","msg":"自推10連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce5cf24438044ccf5bb1b3f9f3d42b23abc2f511","tid":2427244,"uid":61806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T15:58:26.000Z","msg":"自推10連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"600ce365b5dcf00be40fae57a7082805ebe91a6a","tid":2427244,"uid":61806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T15:59:06.000Z","msg":"自推10連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1b53e7fe3cb0b11008fc744b05e9defe27e26d5","tid":2427244,"uid":61806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T15:59:18.000Z","msg":"自推10連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc80075ac855439576c2a5e72604ea85b3772d70","tid":2427244,"uid":61806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T15:59:29.000Z","msg":"自推10連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"016961ba4d04527bcd351f331c335a69dd7cf7ea","tid":2427244,"uid":61806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T16:01:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11999d992337816945ce94d9be7fe7626ab9b55f","tid":2427244,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T16:01:59.000Z","msg":"聽到隔離問醫生嘢你即刻錄音呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08c398eca39b211099cc4d5b0085f5345e20facd","tid":2427244,"uid":61806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"11999d992337816945ce94d9be7fe7626ab9b55f","tid":2427244,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T16:01:59.000Z","msg":"聽到隔離問醫生嘢你即刻錄音呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T16:09:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />是"},{"pid":"a5349562218ab419995da9cd822ce79f553bac10","tid":2427244,"uid":276989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T16:25:18.000Z","msg":"3星期內你係打唔到2劑biotech, 咁打嚟做乜?"},{"pid":"d990536670a76149e893cae77d3699ccd9da0194","tid":2427244,"uid":276989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5349562218ab419995da9cd822ce79f553bac10","tid":2427244,"uid":276989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T16:25:18.000Z","msg":"3星期內你係打唔到2劑biotech, 咁打嚟做乜?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T16:25:52.000Z","msg":"*Biontech"},{"pid":"66b8746d8bc9b8b86a18af019231b28698ecc2f7","tid":2427244,"uid":198389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T16:36:48.000Z","msg":"廢炎後生驚西咩<br />\n專殺啲慢性病廢老肥人<br />\n有得揀一定唔打咩副作用都冇最安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果逼我打打BioNTech算鳩數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22720471db56c26e02884eb159b4fa91d71c9525","tid":2427244,"uid":271851,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T16:40:41.000Z","msg":"唔打住<br />\n1.自己同屋企人都唔係高危人士<br />\n2.唔想做白老鼠<br />\n3.當越多人已打=傳播鏈越少=中招機率越低"}]}